{"type": "article", "id": 8219, "title": "Norm Architects 浴室用品系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-08T07:57:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234546ncAtd9avZpBbYTGx.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t丹麦设计工作室 Norm Architects 最近推出了一个浴室用品系列，包括一个浴缸，一个洗脸盆，一个储物架和一组吊灯。该设计遵循极简主义原则，浴缸和洗脸盆采用同样的形状。整套产品采用一种叫做 “Living Tec”的轻质新型材料，底部则由十字交叉形的黑色支架支撑，简单明快又不失优雅。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052345437ctoVBd9rvqRFePg.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234543yfrKWikFLR6E7hN3.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234543Ei2FwRXh5Hy4Vezd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234544lz0wU6a7EfyvI5ct.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.68148148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234544u6TjU92N4xSykZtW.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.33480176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234545ZsQEBdLz5wlPVU03.jpg\" alt=